16 NEW SECTION. Section 16. Out-of-jurisdiction warrants -- prohibition on own recognizance
17 release. (1) Justices of the peace or judicial officers outside the jurisdiction where a warrant was issued are
18 prohibited from granting an own recognizance or release for a defendant arrested on that warrant.
